    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《幸运之手》是一款Roguelike卡组构建游戏，每抽一张牌都能改变你的命运。构建强力卡组，对抗强敌，探索危险之地。每场战斗后解锁新卡牌，助你踏上冒险旅程！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292920/extras/60cb8aaa2474dabc4d099609bc376c78.poster.avif?t=1772361073\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292920/extras/60cb8aaa2474dabc4d099609bc376c78.webm?t=1772361073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292920/extras/60cb8aaa2474dabc4d099609bc376c78.mp4?t=1772361073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《幸运之手》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《幸运之手》是一款Roguelike卡组构建游戏，在危险的程序生成森林中生存下来需要策略与快速反应。通过每次胜利解锁强大卡牌来构建卡组，并选择独特的英雄参战，每位英雄都有专属技能和能力。每一轮冒险都充满全新挑战和敌人，带来独特且惊险的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292920/extras/863b022de2fbce03ee7df6a5324dd795.poster.avif?t=1772361073\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292920/extras/863b022de2fbce03ee7df6a5324dd795.webm?t=1772361073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292920/extras/863b022de2fbce03ee7df6a5324dd795.mp4?t=1772361073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在险境中战斗时，你将收集升级道具并优化卡组，强化英雄，解锁更多策略选项。无论你是资深策略家还是卡牌新手，《幸运之手》都提供无尽的可重复游玩性和战术深度，每场战斗都将助你掌握构筑卡组的艺术。</p>",
